### 保存用户
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "restful",
  "create_time": "2025-12-20 10:00:00",
  "ext_json": "{\"role\": \"admin\", \"loginCount\": 5}",
  "age": 18,
  "username": "restful"
}

